Bright House Networks LLC Employee Statistics




School/University


Top Degrees


Also Worked at


Time at Bright House Networks LLC

























                                                Applicants across the country flock to Bright House Networks LLC, but positions here are more attractive to alumni from certain universities. Endicott College alumni represent 26.67%, University Of Phoenix speaks for 20%, and University of Phoenix makes up 13.33%.
                                            

                                                Educational trends among employees at Bright House Networks LLC provide insight into the company's intellectual environment. The most common degrees held by Bright House Networks LLC employees are B.S, Associate of Science, and Associate In Science (A.S.
                                            

                                                Applicants seeking opportunities at Bright House Networks LLC have also shown interest in Progress Energy LLC, Consolidated Repair Service, Regions Facility Services, Seminole Electric Cooperative, and Sun Technologies / Guidant Group.
                                            



























